<p>Plus, Multidle offers different puzzle lengths and difficulty levels, so you can challenge yourself in new ways. Give it a try and see how many words you can solve!</p>

<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

<h3>Is "COMET" a hard Wordle answer?</h3>
<p>Compared to some recent Wordles, "comet" is on the easier side. It's a relatively common word, and it doesn't have any unusual letter combinations or obscure meanings. However, it's still possible to get stuck if you don't start with the right letters. </p>

<h3>What does "comet" mean?</h3>
<p>A comet is a celestial object made of ice, dust, and rocky material. When a comet gets close to the Sun, the heat causes the ice to vaporize, creating a glowing head and a long, glowing tail. Comets are often visible in the night sky and are considered a fascinating and beautiful astronomical phenomenon.</p>

<h3>What are the best starting words for Wordle?</h3>
<p>There's no single "best" starting word for Wordle, but some words are generally more helpful than others. Look for words that use common letters like "E," "A," "R," "I," "O," and "T," and that have a good mix of vowels and consonants. Words like "crane," "audio," "stare," and "blitz" are often good choices.</p>

<h3>Can I play Wordle more than once a day?</h3>
<p>No, the official Wordle game only allows one play per day. However, there are many Wordle-like games and websites that let you play as many times as you want.</p>

<h3>Does Wordle ever repeat answers?</h3>
<p>No, Wordle never repeats answers. Each day's puzzle has a unique five-letter word.</p>

<h3>How many possible Wordle answers are there?</h3>
<p>There are 2,315 possible five-letter words in the Wordle answer list.</p>

<h3>What happens if I miss a day in Wordle?</h3>
<p>If you miss a day, you simply won't have a puzzle to solve for that day. Your streak will be broken, but you can start a new one the next day.</p><!----></div><!--]--> <!--[-1--><!--]--></div><!--]--> <!--[-1--><!--]--></div></div><!--]--><!----> <!--[0--><section class="mt-12 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 overflow-hidden"><h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6 flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-2 h-8 bg-green-500 rounded-full"></span> Recent Wordle Answers</h3> <div class="overflow-x-auto"><table class="min-w-full divide-y divide-gray-200 dark:divide-gray-700"><thead class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900"><tr><th class="px-6 py-4 text-left text-xs font-bold text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider">Wordle #</th><th class="px-6 py-4 text-left text-xs font-bold text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider">Date</th><th class="px-6 py-4 text-left text-xs font-bold text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider">Answer</th></tr></thead><tbody class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 divide-y divide-gray-200 dark:divide-gray-700"><!--[--><tr class="transition-colors hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700/50 bg-green-50/50 dark:bg-green-900/10"><td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap text-sm font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">#2564</td><td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">March 30, 2026</td><td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap"><span class="inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-bold bg-green-100 text-green-800 dark:bg-green-900/30 dark:text-green-400">COMET</span></td></tr><tr class="transition-colors hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700/50 "><td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap text-sm font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">#2563</td><td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">March 29, 2026</td><td class="px-6 py-4 white